videos.description: On the second play from scrimmage, Rawleigh Williams III takes the handoff, goes through the line and then turns on the speed to go 72 yards to the end zone putting Arkansas up 7-0 early.
videos.headline: Arkansas wastes no time scoring with 72-yard TD

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald keeps the ball and goes 58 yards untouched to answer Arkansas' long score with a big play score of their own.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald goes for 58-yard TD to answer for Miss. St.

videos.description: Rawleigh Williams III run for 42 yds for a TD
videos.headline: R. Williams III run for 42 yds for a TD

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald run for 18 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Mississippi State QB powers his way to a touchdown

videos.description: Austin Allen pass complete to Keon Hatcher for 5 yds for a TD
videos.headline: A. Allen pass,to K. Hatcher for 5 yds for a TD

videos.description: Rawleigh Williams III run for 7 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Arkansas extends the lead with another rushing touchdown

videos.description: Rawleigh Williams III is lighting up the Mississippi State defense, scoring his fourth touchdown of the game, this time from 33 yards out to give him 190 yards rushing so far.
videos.headline: Williams scores fourth TD... of the first half

videos.description: Arkansas head coach Bret Bielema talks about the play of his running back Rawleigh Williams III
videos.headline: Arkansas head coach Bret Bielema talks about the play of his running back Rawleigh Williams III

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald pass complete to Fred Ross for 40 yds for a TD
videos.headline: N. Fitzgerald pass,to F. Ross for 40 yds for a TD

videos.description: Arkansas's Rawleigh Williams III, already with four touchdowns, gets the handoff on 4th-and-goal, but instead pulls up short and throws it to Austin Cantrell for the touchdown, putting the Razorbacks up 44-21.
videos.headline: Already have 4 rushing TDs? Why not throw for one

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.headline: N. Fitzgerald run for 2 yds for a TD

videos.description: Austin Allen pass complete to Keon Hatcher for 10 yds for a TD
videos.headline: A. Allen pass,to K. Hatcher for 10 yds for a TD

videos.description: While Arkansas' Rawleigh Williams III has four touchdowns, Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald matches him with his fourth running TD in the same game.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald powers in for fourth TD of the game

videos.description: Devwah Whaley run for 4 yds for a TD
